<body>
<div type="letter">
<pb facs="1039116" n="1"/> 
  <note hand="pers_DE-588-119166895"><abbr>NB.</abbr> Deest <rs type="lostletter">epistola</rs> ad <rs type="person">Ritsium</rs> scripta. Ad eundem.</note>
  <p><lb/>Itane tandem, <choice><orig><g ref="#ohat">ô</g></orig><reg>o</reg></choice> optime, et <rs type="letter">liter<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs> tu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> <rs type="place">Basileam</rs> veniunt et <rs type="person">Amicum</rs> de valetudine tua anxium
    <lb/>su<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>a perfundunt l<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>titia. Gratulor vehementer non solum tibi, sed et mihi, ob id quod prosperam
    <lb/>per usum aquarum mineralium recuperaveris salutem, Deus tibi hanc ulterius confirmet, omni<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>aque, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> quilibet bonus sibi optare potest, bona largiatur! Doleo priorem meam <rs type="letter">epistolam</rs>
    <lb/>tibi non fuisse redditam, nec tuam mihi; nescio autem an hoc utrique nostrûm solatium sit,
    <lb/>quod utrumque <rs type="person">Amicus</rs> fefellit, meus certe, cui quod promissis non steterit haud ita pridem
    <lb/>exprobravi, se curavisse ait, ut <rs type="letter">liter<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs> me<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> ad te perferrentur, adeoque pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>ter suam cul<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>pam evenisse, ut deperdit<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> fueri<del><gap/></del><add>n</add>t. <abbr>D.num</abbr> <rs type="person">Burcardum</rs> ad Antistitium evectum esse ne<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>mo mirabitur, nisi qui statum <rs type="place">Civitatis</rs> nostr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> hodiernum ignorat; miror autem, quod
    <lb/>dubites, an munus Professoris Theologi<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> humeris ejus impositum fuerit, cum tamen <choice><orig><g ref="#klammerauf">|:</g></orig><reg>(</reg></choice>ni fal<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>lor<choice><orig><g ref="#klammerzu">:|</g></orig><reg>)</reg></choice> scias, Antistitium cum Professoratu semper conjunctum fuisse, et ad quid, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>so, aliud
    <lb/>ipsi prodesse posset Doctoratus, quam ad Professionem decenter obeundam? sin autem
    <lb/>dubium tuum huc redeat, ut suspiceris, munus Professoris ejus quidem person<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>, humeris
    <lb/>autem alienis impositum esse, tunc tibi illud eximere nequeo, hoc autem dicere possum, quod
    <lb/>paucis post Promotionem diebus <rs type="biblio">Lectionem Inauguralem</rs> habuerit. <rs type="biblio">Oratio</rs> <abbr>Dni</abbr> <rs type="person">Werenfelsii</rs>
    <lb/>Promotoris una cum toto Promotionis actu impressa est sub titulo <rs type="biblio"><hi rend="u">Mitra Aaronis capiti
        <pb facs="1039117" n="2"/>
        <lb/>imposita</hi></rs>, misissem tibi libenter exemplar unum hujus Orationis, sed nullum adhucdum ad me<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>as manus pervenit, quia <abbr>Dn.</abbr> <rs type="person">Antistes</rs> eam in gratiam solum Amicorum suorum imprimi curavit,
    <lb/>ajunt illam apud <rs type="person">Typographum</rs> venalem extare. <rs type="biblio">Dissertationem</rs> ejus inauguralem, quam pe<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tis, nusquam invenire potui; ne indigneris, rationem hujus rei facile conjicere poteris. Sed
    <lb/>properemus ad reliquas Ministrorum Promotiones, audies autem miranda et stupenda, omnis
    <lb/>enim res h<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>c per multas machinationes gesta fuit, inprimis quod Pastoratum et Diacona<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tum Petrinum attinet. Miraberis si cognoveris, <abbr>Dnum</abbr> <rs type="person">Im Hof</rs> pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>ter expectationem
    <lb/>Diaconatum adeptum esse, una cum <rs type="person">filia</rs> <abbr>Dni</abbr> Professoris <rs type="person">Harderi</rs>, intellige <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-1383921512">Augustam</rs>
    <lb/>non viduam <rs type="person">Dni</rs> <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-1383922438">Tonjol<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs>, h<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>c enim nupsit Professori <rs type="person">Battierio</rs> Gr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>co; metuo autem
    <lb/>an sponsalia h<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>c optatum habitura sint exitum, siquidem vicina h<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>c mea non libere
    <lb/>consensit in <rs type="person">Samuelis Prophet<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs> nostri matrimonium. Stupebis vero, et quidem merito,
    <lb/>si dicam, turbas exortas fuisse in electione <abbr>Dni</abbr> <rs type="person">Gernleri</rs> ad Pastoratum, cui et ego in<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>terfui tanquam Candidatus Juris; causa tumultus fuit exclusio <abbr>Dni</abbr> <rs type="person">Huberi</rs> ex ter<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>nario, assumserant enim <abbr>Dni</abbr> Capitulares per pluritatem votorum in ternarium pri<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>mo loco <abbr>D.</abbr> <rs type="person">Battierium</rs> <rs type="place">Albanum</rs>, secundo <abbr>D.</abbr> <rs type="person">Wetstenium</rs> <rs type="place">Leonhardinum</rs>, et tertio
    <lb/><abbr>D.</abbr> <rs type="person">Gernlerum</rs> <rs type="place">Petrinum</rs> Diaconum; contra hunc igitur ternarium publice <choice><orig><g ref="#klammerauf">|:</g></orig><reg>(</reg></choice><abbr>sc.</abbr> in
    <lb/>choro templi, ubi electio Pastoris fieri debebat<choice><orig><g ref="#klammerzu">:|</g></orig><reg>)</reg></choice> protestatus est <abbr>Dn.</abbr> <rs type="person">Huberus</rs> con<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>querens se ex odio privato quorundam, qui in factionem coierant, per fraudulentas
    <lb/>machinationes pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>teritum fuisse, ob quod increpatus fuit ab <rs type="person">Antistite</rs> et <rs type="person">Scholar<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>cha</rs> quodam, sed defensus <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> Tribuno plebis <rs type="person">Burcardo</rs>, hinc ortus tumultus, insur<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>gebant contra seinvicem <rs type="person">Decanus</rs> Capituli, qui pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>sidebat, <rs type="person">Tribunus</rs> plebis, <rs type="person">An<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tistes</rs>, <rs type="person">Scholarch<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs> <abbr><choice><orig><g ref="#etlig">&amp;</g></orig><reg>et</reg></choice>c.</abbr> imo quidam pacis amantes plane secesserunt; sed taceamus
    <lb/>de infandis his et scandalosis rebus, pergamus ad <rs type="person">Pastores</rs> minorum gentium. Avun<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>culus meus <abbr>D.</abbr> <rs type="person">Me<choice><orig><g ref="#ydots">ÿ</g></orig><reg>y</reg></choice>erus</rs> successit <abbr>D.</abbr> <rs type="person">Stöcklino</rs> Pastori in <rs type="place">Oltigen</rs>, qui adeptus est
    <lb/>Pastoratum apud Franciscanos; frater ejus <abbr>D.</abbr> <rs type="person">Joh. S<del><gap/></del><add>t</add>öcklinus</rs> et <rs type="person">Merianus</rs> filius
    <lb/><rs type="person">Pastoris</rs> Diaconatum in <rs type="place">minori Urbe</rs>, alius <rs type="person">Merianus</rs> Pastoratum <rs type="place">Bretzwilan<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice></rs>,
    <lb/><rs type="person">Eulerus</rs> <rs type="place">Riehensem</rs> <rs type="person">Burcardus</rs> <foreign xml:lang="ger">im Würtenberger Hof</foreign> <rs type="place"><abbr>S.</abbr> Jacob<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>um</rs>, <rs type="person">Wildius</rs> 
    <pb facs="1039118" n="3"/> 
    <lb/>olim officio motus <rs type="place">Leuffelfingensem</rs>, <rs type="person">Wetstenius</rs> Pastor in <foreign xml:lang="ger"><rs type="place">Langenbruckh</rs></foreign> <rs type="place">Rimlingensem</rs>,
    <lb/><rs type="person">Friburgerus</rs> <rs type="place">Langenbruggensem</rs>, et denique <rs type="person">Burcardus</rs> filius <rs type="person">Pastoris</rs> in <rs type="place">Rothenflueh</rs>
    <lb/>Vicariatum et certam <rs type="person">Patri</rs> suo succedendi spem consecuti sunt; et h<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> sunt mutatio<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>nes ill<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> anno abhinc in Ministerio contigerunt. <rs type="biblio">Concionem</rs> <abbr>D.</abbr> <rs type="person">Werenfelsii</rs>, quam
    <lb/>petiisti, misi <abbr>D.</abbr> <rs type="person">Zörnlino</rs> una cum exemplari aliquo <rs type="biblio">Dissertationis</rs> me<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>, ut prioris, si
    <lb/>forte deperdita fuisset <choice><orig><g ref="#klammerauf">|:</g></orig><reg>(</reg></choice>eam enim te nondum accepisse ex tuis et <abbr>D.</abbr> <rs type="person">Zörnlini</rs> <rs type="letter">literis</rs> co<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>gnovi<choice><orig><g ref="#klammerzu">:|</g></orig><reg>)</reg></choice> vicem sustinere posset. Tibi forsan jam nuntiatum erit, Germanorum temera<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>riam territorii nostri violationem multum inco<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>odi nobis fecisse, adeo ut <rs type="place">foedera<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>torum Cantonum</rs> milites pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>sidiarios hic habere coacti simus. Sed sat prata biberunt.</p>
<closer>Vale, amice optime, et amare perge tuum, qui te millies salvere jubet, <signed>NB.</signed> <dateline><date when="1709">1709</date><!--Tag und Monat müssen noch ausgezeichnet werden.--></dateline>.</closer>
</div>
</body>
